{"type":"message","id":"b4a4e597","parentId":"f1ee0617","timestamp":"2026-03-08T06:00:32.073Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:7f5c72af-c773-419f-a41b-2bb90c810972 虾王群消息总结] 用 tenant_access_token（应用身份，不要用 user_access_token）调用飞书 Open API GET /open-apis/im/v1/messages，参数 container_id_type=chat，container_id=oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569，拉取过去1小时内的所有消息。拿到消息后，用虾王殿下的语气生成总结，包括主要话题、重要结论、需要苏神关注的事项。如果这一小时没有有价值的内容就不发。\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 8th, 2026 — 2:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772949632069}}
{"type":"message","id":"7bbd6dd9","parentId":"b4a4e597","timestamp":"2026-03-08T06:00:46.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"苏神，本王来帮你处理这个定时任务！首先得搞清楚怎么用 tenant_access_token 调用飞书 API 拉取群消息对吧？\n\n让本王先看看工作区里有没有相关的脚本或者配置文件~"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_laln2h96a08wno97gkg0rtgp","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace","workdir":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":36883,"output":121,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37004,"cost":{"input":0.0000036883000000000003,"output":2.42e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000037125000000000005}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772949632071}}
